# API Routes Context

## Purpose and Responsibilities
- RESTful API endpoints for the application
- Request validation and error handling
- Authentication and authorization
- Data transformation and response formatting

## Dependencies
### External
- next
- zod (for validation)
- @supabase/supabase-js

### Internal
- @/lib/supabase
- @/services/*
- @/types/common

## API Structure
- `/auth/*` - Authentication endpoints
- `/posts/*` - Post management endpoints
- `/users/*` - User management endpoints
- `/messages/*` - Chat/messaging endpoints
- `/payments/*` - Payment processing endpoints

## State Management Approach
- Stateless API endpoints
- Request/response validation
- Error handling middleware

## Related Services
- All endpoints use corresponding service functions

## Testing Approach
- API endpoint testing with Jest
- Request/response validation testing
- Authentication flow testing
